HELLO.

00:19.587 --> 00:21.155
NO, GEORGE.
NO MORE CUTBACKS.

00:21.155 --> 00:23.157
IN FACT,
THIS PLAN HAS EVERYTHING

00:23.157 --> 00:24.758
YOU AND THE WORKERS WANTED.

00:24.758 --> 00:26.760
THERE'S JUST, YOU KNOW,
ONE LITTLE CATCH.

00:26.760 --> 00:29.763
YOU GOTTA TELL 'EM THAT
IN ORDER TO AFFORD THIS,

00:29.763 --> 00:31.965
