A SUBCONTRACTOR.

00:47.948 --> 00:49.617
I LOVE THOSE GUYS.

00:49.617 --> 00:54.122
JACK, THESE ARE THE SAME GUYS
THAT APPROVED THONG THURSDAY.

00:56.390 --> 00:59.427
YOU WANT TO SEE ERNIE COME
TO WORK LIKE THAT AGAIN?

00:59.427 --> 01:01.395
