NO, I SMOKE BECAUSE GEORGE
IS A WHINY LITTLE GIRL.

12:46.366 --> 12:49.569
THAT DOCTOR DIDN'T KNOW WHAT
THE HELL HE WAS TALKING ABOUT.

12:49.569 --> 12:51.304
HE WASN'T EVEN A REAL DOCTOR.

12:51.304 --> 12:53.974
I TRIED TO SHOW HIM
THE MOLE ON MY BACK.

12:53.974 --> 12:56.409
HE WAS LIKE, "SIR,
PLEASE PULL YOUR PANTS UP."

12:56.409 --> 13:00.747
WHY DO YOU SHOW THAT THING
TO EVERYBODY?

13:00.747 --> 13:02.549
SHE WAS
A HORRIBLE MOTHER,

13:02.549 --> 13:05.218
BUT I'M THE BAD GUY
FOR COMPLAINING ABOUT IT.

13:05.218 --> 13:07.354
I AGREE. SHE WAS AWFUL.

13:07.354 --> 13:10.958
BUT IF THE DOCTOR SAYS
THAT YOU'RE MAKING HER SMOKE,

13:10.958 --> 13:13.026
MAYBE YOU CAN
CUT HER SOME SLACK.

13:13.026 --> 13:15.162
DO YOU REALLY
HAVE TO COMPLAIN?

13:15.162 --> 13:17.164
YES, BECAUSE NOW I CAN.

13:17.164 --> 13:19.166
WHEN I WAS A KID,
EVERY TIME I COMPLAINED,

13:19.166 --> 13:21.134
SHE'D SMACK ME
UPSIDE THE HEAD

13:21.134 --> 13:24.304
AND SAY, "THANK YOU FOR VISITING
THE COMPLAINT DEPARTMENT."

13:24.304 --> 13:27.007
IT WAS THE ONLY DEPARTMENT
IN HER STORE,

13:27.007 --> 13:30.277
AND IT DRANK A LOT.

13:30.277 --> 13:33.613
THAT WAS A LONG TIME AGO,

13:33.613 --> 13:37.184
A-AND THERE'S SOMETHING
MORE IMPORTANT HAPPENING HERE.

13:37.184 --> 13:40.153
WE ALL KNOW WHERE
THE SMOKING IS LEADING TO.

13:40.153 --> 13:42.155
DO YOU REALLY WANT
TO WATCH YOUR MOM

13:42.155 --> 13:44.291
DIE A SLOW, PAINFUL DEATH?

13:45.458 --> 13:47.460
IF HER EYES ROLL BACK
IN HER HEAD

13:47.460 --> 13:49.496
AND HER ARMS SHAKE
LIKE A LITTLE BUG,

13:49.496 --> 13:52.299
YEAH, I'D LIKE TO SEE THAT.
GEORGE.

13:52.299 --> 13:54.367
FOR THE FIRST TIME
IN HER LIFE,

13:54.367 --> 13:57.370
YOUR MOTHER HAS A REAL REASON
TO QUIT, A-AND IF YOU HELP HER,

13:57.370 --> 13:59.372
IT WON'T JUST
BE GOOD FOR HER,

13:59.372 --> 14:01.608
IT'LL BE EMOTIONALLY HEALTHY
FOR YOU.

14:01.608 --> 14:02.910
BUT I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

14:02.910 --> 14:05.445
WHY DO I HAVE
TO BE EMOTIONALLY HEALTHY?

14:05.445 --> 14:08.615
BECAUSE
IT'S THE RIGHT THING TO DO.

14:11.551 --> 14:12.685
MOM?

14:12.685 --> 14:14.054
YEAH?

14:14.054 --> 14:17.657
ARE, UH... YOU STILL GONNA
TRY TO QUIT SMOKING?

14:17.657 --> 14:18.858
(sniffs)

14:18.858 --> 14:20.660
NO, I WANT TO LOSE A JOB

14:20.660 --> 14:24.031
AND LIVE IN A SMALL BOX
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE ROAD.

14:24.031 --> 14:26.366
WHAT KIND OF A DUMB QUESTION
IS THAT?

14:27.800 --> 14:29.937
OKAY, UH, HERE'S THE DEAL.

14:29.937 --> 14:32.205
I'M GONNA TRY
TO STOP COMPLAINING

14:32.205 --> 14:35.208
BECAUSE I DON'T WANT
TO BE YOUR EXCUSE FOR SMOKING.

14:35.208 --> 14:38.211
SO IF YOU CAN'T QUIT,

14:38.211 --> 14:40.213
IT'S 'CAUSE YOU'RE
SELF-DESTRUCTIVE, UNDISCIPLINED,

14:40.213 --> 14:41.915
AND YOU NEVER GAVE ME
A BIRTHDAY PARTY

14:41.915 --> 14:44.985
WHEN I WAS A KID!
GEORGE.

14:44.985 --> 14:46.987
STARTING NOW.

14:46.987 --> 14:49.489
YOU'RE GONNA TRY?
HA! GOOD LUCK.

14:49.489 --> 14:53.526
I WATCHED YOU TRY TO LEARN
TO SKATEBOARD, RIDE A BIKE,

14:53.526 --> 14:55.262
USE A TOILET.

14:55.262 --> 14:58.665
YOU FELL OVER
AND HIT YOUR HEAD EVERY TIME.

14:58.665 --> 15:01.301
WELL,
WHAT CAN I SAY, MOM?

15:01.301 --> 15:03.436
I WAS A CLUMSY LITTLE BOY.

15:03.436 --> 15:06.473
BUT, YOU KNOW, IF YOU WANT
TO TRY IT, GO FOR IT.

15:06.473 --> 15:07.607
FINE WITH ME.

15:07.607 --> 15:10.610
IT WOULD BE SO NICE
NOT TO HAVE TO LISTEN

15:10.610 --> 15:13.913
TO A GROWN MAN COMPLAIN
LIKE A 3 YEAR OLD.

15:13.913 --> 15:15.782
HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT?

15:15.782 --> 15:17.584
PICK ME UP TOMORROW
AT 8:00.

15:17.584 --> 15:20.353
OH, AND TRY NOT
TO FALL OFF THE CAN.

15:20.353 --> 15:24.624
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO HIT YOUR HEAD AND FORGET.

15:32.565 --> 15:35.969
HEY. MAN, IT'S NICE TO GO
DOWN TO THE LOADING DOCK

15:35.969 --> 15:38.038
AND NOT HAVE TO SMELL
CIGARETTE SMOKE.

15:38.038 --> 15:40.040
NOW IT'S JUST TRUCK EXHAUST

15:40.040 --> 15:42.042
AND, UH, THE FUMES
FROM THAT GREEN STUFF

15:42.042 --> 15:44.777
THE GOVERNMENT
WON'T LET US THROW AWAY.

15:44.777 --> 15:46.146
MMM. MM-HMM.

15:46.146 --> 15:48.715
OH, YOU MUST HAVE GOT
THE LAST FRUIT PIE.

15:48.715 --> 15:50.750
THE VENDING MACHINE'S
ALL SOLD OUT.

15:50.750 --> 15:53.453
THE WORKERS CAN'T SMOKE,
SO THEY'RE EATING.

15:53.453 --> 15:54.787
OH.

15:54.787 --> 15:57.824
HEY, SO HOW'S IT GOING
WITH NOT INSULTING YOUR MOM?

15:57.824 --> 16:00.527
WELL, YOU KNOW, IT'S BEEN
TWO WEEKS, AND IT...

16:00.527 --> 16:02.529
(sniffs)
GETS EASIER ALL THE TIME.

16:02.529 --> 16:05.098
YOU JUST NEED DISCIPLINE
AND SELF-CONTROL.

16:12.039 --> 16:14.207
MAN, LOOK AT ALL THESE
FRUIT PIE WRAPPERS.

16:15.975 --> 16:18.978
YOU ATE THEM ALL!

16:20.880 --> 16:23.816
Ã³RALE, C.S. PIE.

16:23.816 --> 16:26.986
GO INVESTIGATE
SOMEONE ELSE.

16:32.659 --> 16:35.495
IT'S 11:00, AND YOU'RE JUST
PUNCHING IN NOW?

16:35.495 --> 16:41.634
OH. I HAD ONE OF MY REALLY,
REALLY BAD NIGHTS, GEORGE.

16:41.634 --> 16:44.304
I KEPT HAVING THIS NIGHTMARE
THAT THIS FAT-HEADED KID

16:44.304 --> 16:49.842
KEPT CRYING, "PLAY WITH ME.
PLAY WITH ME,"

16:49.842 --> 16:53.380
AND ALL I WANTED WAS TO HAVE
A CIGARETTE AND SMACK HIM.

16:53.380 --> 16:56.183
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS.

16:56.183 --> 16:58.017
IT MEANS THAT, YOU KNOW,

16:58.017 --> 17:01.754
YOU'RE FIGHTING AN ADDICTION,
AND IT'S OKAY THAT YOU'RE LATE.

17:01.754 --> 17:03.123
EXCUSE ME.

17:06.893 --> 17:08.228
(machine beeps)

17:08.228 --> 17:11.498
OH, NO, GEORGE.
GEORGE, STOP!

17:11.498 --> 17:14.701
THIS IS EMOTIONAL EATING, OKAY?
I USED TO BE BIG. I KNOW.

17:14.701 --> 17:17.437
YOU'RE EATING BECAUSE YOU'RE
STRESSED OUT ABOUT YOUR MOM.

17:17.437 --> 17:19.439
I'M NOT STRESSED OUT, MAN.
I'M JUST HUNGRY.

17:19.439 --> 17:20.740
MIND YOUR OWN BUSINESS.

17:20.740 --> 17:22.975
OH, THIS IS SO GOOD,
I CAN'T BELIEVE.

17:22.975 --> 17:26.012
GEORGE, GEORGE, I NEED FOR YOU
TO ADD THIS INVOICE, OKAY?

17:26.012 --> 17:27.580
IT'S GONNA BE OVER TEN,

17:27.580 --> 17:31.151
SO I'LL WAIT WHILE YOU TAKE OFF
YOUR SHOES AND SOCKS.

17:31.151 --> 17:33.320
YOU MISERABLE, OLD--

17:33.320 --> 17:35.922
HUH. I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT
RIGHT NOW.

17:35.922 --> 17:37.824
I'LL TAKE THOSE.

17:37.824 --> 17:40.827
HEY, THERE'S NOTHING BUT APPLES
AND PEARS IN THERE.

17:40.827 --> 17:44.331
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO EAT?
WHAT'S WITH HIM?

17:44.331 --> 17:47.734
I THINK IT'S YOU.

17:47.734 --> 17:49.102
YEAH.

17:49.102 --> 17:51.404
HE'S EATING
TO STUFF DOWN HIS FEELINGS

17:51.404 --> 17:53.706
BECAUSE HE DOESN'T WANT
TO INSULT YOU.

17:53.706 --> 17:56.676
HEY, I DIDN'T ASK HIM
TO DO THAT.

17:56.676 --> 17:58.678
YOU KNOW,
I'VE KNOWN YOU A LONG TIME,

17:58.678 --> 18:01.948
AND I'VE NEVER TOLD YOU THIS,
BUT YOU'RE A COLD WOMAN.

18:01.948 --> 18:03.316
HUH?

18:03.316 --> 18:05.318
YOUR SON
IS EATING HIMSELF SICK

18:05.318 --> 18:08.288
TO TRY AND KEEP YOU FROM KILLING
YOURSELF WITH CIGARETTES,

18:08.288 --> 18:10.623
AND YOU DON'T EVEN
APPRECIATE IT.

18:10.623 --> 18:14.694
YOU KNOW, UM, MY LUNGS
ARE WORKING AGAIN...

18:16.062 --> 18:19.399
AND I CAN RUN YOU DOWN
LIKE A DOG.

18:19.399 --> 18:21.768
YEAH, WELL,
IT'S JUST A THEORY.

18:21.768 --> 18:23.203
I'LL CATCH YOU LATER.

18:38.785 --> 18:43.690
I CAN'T TAKE IT ANYMORE!

18:43.690 --> 18:45.725
I'M LIGHTING UP.

18:48.695 --> 18:50.630
MOM,
WHAT THE HELL YOU DOING?

18:50.630 --> 18:53.166
(sighs)
I'M GETTING FIRED.

18:53.166 --> 18:55.835
I AM WHO I AM, GEORGE.

18:55.835 --> 18:57.304
I'M A SMOKER.

18:57.304 --> 18:59.172
IT'S MORE THAN
AN ADDICTION.

18:59.172 --> 19:00.640
IT'S A LIFESTYLE CHOICE,

19:00.640 --> 19:04.411
LIKE BEING A CROSS-DRESSER
OR--OR A TERRORIST.

19:04.411 --> 19:06.713
BUT YOU'VE BEEN HERE
FOR 40 YEARS.

19:06.713 --> 19:08.715
I MEAN,
WHERE YOU GONNA GO?

19:08.715 --> 19:11.318
OH, COME ON.
I'LL FIND ANOTHER JOB.

19:11.318 --> 19:12.652
I'LL JUST LIVE CHEAPER.

19:12.652 --> 19:15.855
I JUST KNOW THAT I GOTTA
GET OUT OF HERE, GEORGE.

19:15.855 --> 19:17.657
BOY, I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

19:17.657 --> 19:19.792
IT'S BEEN PURE HELL
THESE LAST FEW WEEKS.

19:19.792 --> 19:22.862
NOW YOU KNOW WHAT THE FIRST
18 YEARS OF MY LIFE WERE LIKE,

19:22.862 --> 19:25.998
YOU BITTER OLD TROLL!

19:25.998 --> 19:28.835
OH, THAT FELT SO GOOD!

19:28.835 --> 19:33.172
ALL RIGHT.
EVERYTHING IS BACK TO NORMAL.

19:33.172 --> 19:36.309
NOW YOU CAN STOP
STUFFING YOUR FACE.

19:38.345 --> 19:39.712
WAIT A MINUTE.

19:39.712 --> 19:43.182
YOU'RE NOT QUITTING
SO YOU CAN SMOKE.

19:43.182 --> 19:45.385
YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT ME.

19:45.385 --> 19:48.255
YES, IT'S ALL ABOUT YOU.

19:50.690 --> 19:53.260
WHY DOES THE SUN RISE
IN THE MORNING?

19:53.260 --> 19:55.695
BECAUSE GEORGE
IS AFRAID OF THE DARK.

19:55.695 --> 19:58.231
YOU KNOW, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO LEAVE, MOM.

19:58.231 --> 20:01.434
I MEAN, IT'S BEEN TOUGH NOT
BEING ABLE TO INSULT YOU,

20:01.434 --> 20:02.735
BUT, YOU KNOW,

20:02.735 --> 20:05.137
I'LL FIND A WAY
TO DEAL WITH IT.

20:05.137 --> 20:07.407
HOW? LOOK AT YOU.

20:07.407 --> 20:09.576
YOUR POCKETS
ARE STUFFED WITH CANDY.

20:09.576 --> 20:12.812
YOU GOT PIE
ALL OVER YOUR FACE.

20:12.812 --> 20:16.215
YOU'RE NOT A MAN ANYMORE.
YOU'RE A TRICK-OR-TREATER.

20:18.017 --> 20:20.086
SIT DOWN.

20:20.086 --> 20:23.523
LET'S TALK.
COME ON.

20:23.523 --> 20:25.592
LET'S BE HONEST,
GEORGE.

20:25.592 --> 20:28.961
WE HAVE BEEN THE WAY WE ARE
FOR OVER 40 YEARS.

20:28.961 --> 20:30.763
WE'RE NOT GONNA CHANGE NOW.

20:30.763 --> 20:32.699
I MEAN,
YOU KNOW, WHO KNOWS?

20:32.699 --> 20:34.734
MAYBE NOT BEING AROUND YOU
ALL THE TIME,

20:34.734 --> 20:37.737
IT'LL BE EASIER FOR ME
TO QUIT SMOKING.

20:37.737 --> 20:40.673
YOU'RE REALLY GONNA
LEAVE THE FACTORY?

20:43.109 --> 20:44.544
YEAH.

20:46.946 --> 20:48.214
HEY.

20:48.214 --> 20:51.984
I KNOW YOU REALLY
CAN'T SAY IT, BUT...

20:51.984 --> 20:54.854
I KNOW WHY YOU'RE DOING THIS.
THANKS, MOM.

20:56.856 --> 20:59.526
I CAN SAY IT.

20:59.526 --> 21:03.530
GEORGIE, THE TRUTH IS,

21:03.530 --> 21:06.733
WITH ALL THE CRAP
I'VE GONE THROUGH IN MY LIFE,

21:06.733 --> 21:09.536
THERE'S REALLY
ONLY ONE THING

21:09.536 --> 21:12.038
THAT'S EVER
BROUGHT ME HAPPINESS.

21:12.038 --> 21:13.773
YOU DON'T HAVE TO SAY IT.

21:13.773 --> 21:15.975
CIGARETTES.

21:20.580 --> 21:22.549
THAT'S WHY I DIDN'T
WANT YOU TO SAY IT.
